	<AC_SizeCostScaling>Size-Based Cost Scaling</AC_SizeCostScaling>
	<AC_SizeCostScalingTooltip>Scales resource costs based on the size of the pawn being converted.</AC_SizeCostScalingTooltip>
	<AC_PrintTimeMultiplier>Print Time Multiplier</AC_PrintTimeMultiplier>
